{
  "stem": "2230.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then the few of us who were in the village decided to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] do something, see something-- see where you are, what you come, what you do.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were-- what part of the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew it was Teplice-Sanov, who knew?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On the German Czech border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So we started to-- to walk, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and from village to village.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were lucky we found a lot of bicycles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, the German soldiers didn't want to be caught, and if you were caught with a German bicycle, they knew that you were a soldier.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they would drop the bicycles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would pick them up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember I had one, and we just peddled.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Plain clothes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To be honest with you, we [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] stole a lot of clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember one thing that I'll never forget, and until today I feel bad about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I stole a suitcase full of stamps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I gave it away later, but I stole it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What were stamps?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never saw a stamp in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never mailed a letter in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never wrote a letter in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a suitcase full of-- I picked it up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the back of the bicycles, there were, like, luggage things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Funny, you know, it reminded me-- those stamps [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was passage to the United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I came illegally, but it was passage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we travelled--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
